ural%20lighting&width=800&height=600&seq=industry-hemp-001&orientation=landscape",description:"We help hemp brands establish strong online presence and dominate organic search results. Our Hemp SEO Agency specializes in building topical authority for hemp-related keywords, creating compliant content that educates consumers, and implementing technical SEO strategies that improve visibility. From hemp clothing to hemp supplements, we understand the unique challenges of marketing hemp products and develop customized strategies that drive qualified traffic and increase conversions. Our approach includes comprehensive keyword research, competitor analysis, content optimization, and strategic link building within the hemp industry ecosystem.",cta:"Grow Your Hemp Brand"},{name:"CBD Stores",icon:"ri-store-line",image:"https://readdy.ai/api/search-image?query=modern%20CBD%20store%20interior%20with%20premium%20product%20displays%2C%20wellness%20atmosphere%2C%20professional%20retail%20photography%2C%20clean%20organized%20shelving%2C%20natural%20lighting%20and%20green%20accents&width=800&height=600&seq=industry-cbd-002&orientation=landscape",description:"CBD ecommerce requires specialized SEO strategies that account for payment processing restrictions, advertising limitations, and compliance requirements. Our Hemp SEO Agency has extensive experience optimizing CBD stores for maximum organic visibility and revenue growth. We implement advanced ecommerce SEO techniques including product schema markup, category optimization, internal linking strategies, and conversion rate optimization. Our team understands how to navigate Google Shopping restrictions, optimize product pages for featured snippets, and create content that builds trust with potential customers. We also specialize in local SEO for brick-and-mortar CBD stores, helping you dominate local search results and drive foot traffic.",cta:"Optimize Your CBD Store"},{name:"Dispensaries",icon:"ri-hospital-line",image:"https://readdy.ai/api/search-image?query=professional%20cannabis%20dispensary%20interior%2C%20modern%20retail%20design%2C%20secure%20professional%20atmosphere%2C%20product%20display%20cases%2C%20clean%20contemporary%20architecture%20with%20natural%20elements&width=800&height=600&seq=industry-dispensary-003&orientation=landscape",description:"Dispensary SEO requires hyper-local optimization strategies and deep understanding of state-specific cannabis regulations. Our Hemp SEO Agency specializes in helping dispensaries dominate local search results through comprehensive Google Business Profile optimization, local citation building, and location-specific content creation. We develop SEO strategies that account for varying state laws, implement schema markup for dispensaries, and create content that educates consumers while maintaining compliance. Our services include multi-location SEO for dispensary chains, review management, local link building, and geo-targeted landing pages. We help dispensaries increase foot traffic, online orders, and brand awareness in their local markets.",cta:"Dominate Local Search"},{name:"Vape Shops",icon:"ri-mist-line",image:"https://readdy.ai/api/search-image?query=modern%20vape%20shop%20interior%20with%20product%20displays%2C%20contemporary%20retail%20design%2C%20vaping%20devices%20and%20accessories%20showcase%2C%20professional%20commercial%20photography%2C%20clean%20organized%20space&width=800&height=600&seq=industry-vape-004&orientation=landscape",description:"Vape shop SEO faces unique challenges with advertising restrictions and evolving regulations. Our Hemp SEO Agency has proven experience helping vape shops increase organic visibility and drive qualified traffic. We implement comprehensive SEO strategies including technical optimization, content marketing, local SEO, and link building specifically tailored for the vape industry. Our team understands how to optimize for vape-related keywords while maintaining compliance with platform guidelines. We create educational content that positions your vape shop as an authority, optimize product pages for conversions, and build local citations that improve your visibility in local search results. Whether you operate a single location or multiple vape shops, we develop scalable SEO strategies that deliver measurable results.",cta:"Boost Your Vape Shop"}];return d.jsx("section",{id:"industries",className:"py-20 bg-white",children:d.jsxs("div",{className:"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8",children:[d.jsxs("div",{className:"text-center mb-16",children:[d.jsx("h2",{className:"font-['Playfair_Display'] text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-[#1A3C34] mb-4",children:"Industries We Serve"}),d.jsx("p",{className:"text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto",children:"Specialized Hemp SEO Agency expertise across all cannabis-related industries"})]}),d.jsx("div",{className:"flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 mb-12",children:r.map((u,c)=>d.jsxs("button",{onClick:()=>a(c),className:`px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-all cursor-pointer whitespace-nowrap flex items-center gap-2 ${s===c?"bg-[#1A3C34] text-white shadow-lg":"bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-200"}`,children:[d.jsx("i",{className:`${u.icon} text-xl`}),u.name]},c))}),d.jsx("div",{className:"bg-[#F8F9FA] rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-xl",children:d.jsxs("div",{className:"grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-0",children:[d.jsx("div",{className:"w-full h-96 lg:h-auto",children:d.jsx("img",{src:r[s].image,alt:r[s].name,className:"w-full h-full object-cover object-top"})}),d.jsxs("div",{className:"p-8 lg:p-12 flex flex-col justify-center",children:[d.jsx("div",{className:"w-16 h-16 bg-[#A8D5BA] rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6",children:d.jsx("i",{className:`${r[s].icon} text-4xl text-[#1A3C34]`})}),d.jsx("h3",{className:"text-3xl font-bold text-[#1A3C34] mb-6",children:r[s].name}),d.jsx("p",{className:"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-8",children:r[s].description}),d.jsx("a",{href:"#contact",c