livered beyond expectations. We now rank #1 in all our target cities, and foot traffic has increased dramatically. Their understanding of cannabis regulations and local search is unmatched."},{name:"Jennifer Rodriguez",role:"Marketing Director, Hemp Wellness Co",image:"https://readdy.ai/api/search-image?query=professional%20businesswoman%20marketing%20director%20portrait%2C%20confident%20professional%2C%20modern%20office%20background%2C%20corporate%20headshot%20photography%2C%20natural%20lighting&width=200&height=200&seq=testimonial-003&orientation=squarish",rating:5,text:"Finally, an SEO agency that gets the hemp industry! Their strategic approach to content and link building has positioned us as an authority in our niche. We have seen consistent month-over-month growth in rankings, traffic, and most importantly, revenue."},{name:"David Thompson",role:"Founder, Vape Nation",image:"https://readdy.ai/api/search-image?query=professional%20businessman%20founder%20portrait%2C%20entrepreneurial%20confident%2C%20modern%20office%20setting%2C%20corporate%20headshot%20photography%2C%20natural%20lighting&width=200&height=200&seq=testimonial-004&orientation=squarish",rating:5,text:"The results speak for themselves. Our vape shop went from struggling to find customers online to being the top result for dozens of high-value keywords. The Hemp SEO Agency team is responsive, transparent, and delivers real ROI."},{name:"Amanda Foster",role:"Owner, Pure CBD Store",image:"https://readdy.ai/api/search-image?query=professional%20businesswoman%20owner%20portrait%2C%20warm%20friendly%20smile%2C%20modern%20office%20background%2C%20corporate%20headshot%20photography%2C%20natural%20lighting&width=200&height=200&seq=testimonial-005&orientation=squarish",rating:5,text:"I have worked with several SEO agencies before, but none understood the unique challenges of CBD ecommerce like this team. They optimized our entire site, created amazing content, and built quality backlinks. Our sales have inc