cy can), we do guarantee our proven process and transparent reporting. Our Hemp SEO Agency has a 98% success rate in achieving page 1 rankings for target keywords within 6-12 months. We focus on sustainable, white-hat strategies that deliver long-term results."},{question:"Is Hemp SEO compliant with Google guidelines?",answer:"Absolutely. Compliance is our top priority. We stay current with all Google guidelines, state regulations, and industry best practices. Our content strategies are designed to educate and inform while maintaining full compliance. We have a 98% compliance rate and have never had a client penalized for our SEO work."},{question:"What industries do you serve?",answer:"Our Hemp SEO Agency specializes in hemp brands, CBD stores, cannabis dispensaries, vape shops, and related wellness businesses. We have extensive experience with both ecommerce and brick-and-mortar businesses in the cannabis industry."},{question:"How much does Hemp SEO cost?",answer:"Our pricing varies based on your specific needs, competition level, and business goals. We offer customized packages starting at $2,500/month for small businesses and scaling up for larger enterprises. Every package includes comprehensive SEO services, transparent reporting, and dedicated account management. Contact us for a free audit and custom quote."},{question:"Can you help with Google Ads for CBD products?",answer:"Yes! We specialize in compliant Google Ads strategies for CBD and hemp products. While Google restricts most cannabis-related advertising, we have proven methods for running successful campaigns within platform guidelines. Our approach includes alternative keyword targeting, compliant landing pages, and strategic campaign structures."},{question:"Do you offer local SEO for dispensaries?",answer:"Absolutely. Local SEO is one of our core specialties. We help dispensaries dominate local search through Google Business Profile optimization, local citation building, location-specific landing 